trans-unit.target: TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> The inattentive culinarian dearly hopes his international delivery hasn't been lost at sea.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TODO_00<tab>Speak with the diligent deckhand.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TODO_01<tab>Pick up the shipment for Aunt Tii's.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the shipment for Aunt Tii's to the inattentive culinarian.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TODO_03<tab>Speak with the inattentive culinarian.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_001<tab>You were on the ship that pulled into port just now, were you not? I've a favor to ask.

TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_002<tab>I'm expecting a shipment addressed to Aunt Tii's Tacos, but I fear it may have been unloaded on the southern pier by mistake. I'd be ever so grateful if you could speak with your crew for me.

TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_003<tab>I need to be getting back to open the shop, but if you do manage to find it, please bring it over. I'll see to it you're paid for the delivery, I promise!
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SAILOR05019_000_010<tab>A shipment for Aunt Tii's? Got it right here, o' course. Not sure what you were told, but all imports from Eorzea are unloaded on this side.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SAILOR05019_000_011<tab>That culinarian makes some great tacos, but I'll be damned if he can pay attention to half the words I say to him...
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SAILOR05019_000_012<tab>His order's packed and ready in that crate there, but bugger me if it ain't heavy.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Carry the shipment to the inattentive culinarian at Aunt Tii's Tacos before the time runs out.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SYSTEM_000_014<tab>You will have 120 seconds to complete the task. Should you fail, return to the starting location and begin anew.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SAILOR05019_000_020<tab>Right, that's the crate for Aunt Tii's. It's not far from here, if you don't mind carryin' it over.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_SAILOR05019_000_021<tab>What'd I tell you? Remember, lift with your legs!
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_025<tab>You haven't found my shipment? Could you try asking around?
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_030<tab>You found it! Thank the gods. I don't know what I would have done had my cookbooks been left on the dock back in Limsa Lominsa.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_100_030<tab>What luck that I could flag down such a hospitable deckhand.
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_031<tab>Wait─what do you mean, you're not part of the crew!? I thought you came into port with my books!

TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_032<tab>Our taco stand gets a lot of tourists, so I thought I'd import some cookbooks from your culinary capital and brush up on foreign food culture. Who knows─one of these days I might just invent an Eorzean-style taco!
TEXT_KINGZA003_05019_TACOSCHEF05019_000_033<tab>Anyway, my apologies for the misunderstanding! As payment, take these freshly made tacos, on the house!
